{"tid":846394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國財政部在港發行45億元人民幣國債","createTime":"2018-10-03T11:27:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T11:42:07.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"49b824a03aa8adeb7749871b8cf90911495dc0ef","tid":846394,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:27:19.000Z","msg":"中國財政部表示，透過香港金管局的債務工具中央結算系統發行45億元人民幣國債，將於下周三進行投標，下周五交收。<br />\n<br />\n其中總額為30億元的2020國債，年利率為3.65%，另外15億元的2023國債年利率為3.8%。<br />\n<br />\n財政部委任交通銀行香港分行作為發行及交存代理，負責協助財政部辦理增發國債招標。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421166-20181003.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421166-20181003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8sSJMwHtD4KL2qumG5YIRsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=efb19679\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1421166-20181003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=81cc2266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1421166-20181003.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"0204791c12c9f436a803e8ba2ed0424d694aa776","tid":846394,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"終於來了 營富基金出動"},{"pid":"7918b736a2f102f0a0d73b19e032953d606424d3","tid":846394,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:30:24.000Z","msg":"美元結算既話 有20%機會會諗下既<em></em>"},{"pid":"d89547721d79779317f7c49e9037265d932b5143","tid":846394,"uid":26752,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"山窮水盡要黎香港開刀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065fbe2deb13d4969ee11dab3fc95f6f75885d03","tid":846394,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0204791c12c9f436a803e8ba2ed0424d694aa776","tid":846394,"uid":58552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T11:28